Class Enclosures

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.ov.sdk.dto.generated.Enclosures

    @Generated(value="org.jsonschema2pojo")
public class Enclosures
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The Enclosures data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent a enclosure in the system. It is passed in to the add/update enclosure REST api, as well as the add/update enclosure through java client api.
